 19. Gin2-na2 oe7 chhio7 Kng 
 Bou2 sou2-chai7 u7 chit8 e5 chap8 he3 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 teh khau tiaN2. I e5 mia5 kio3 Bong2-chhi7. Gin2-na2 e5 lau7-bu2 si7 song3-hiong lang5 sou2-i2 Bong2-chhi7 kap lang5 toa3 tau3 kha-chhiu2 thang than3 tam7-poh8 chiN5. 
 TiaN2 e5 ian-thun5 chin ou, ku2-ku2 bo5 khau. Sui si7 an2-ni i bo5 hiam5 kan-khou2, hoaN-hi2 chhut siaN gim5 si kong2, 
 “Ia5-sou kio3 lan2 lang5, Choe3 chin kng e5 teng; Chhin-chhiuN7 chit8 ki chek he2, Mi5-si5 chio3 kng-beng5; Chit se3-kan si7 ou-am3, Na2 chhin-chhiuN7 ou-bak8; Lan2 tioh8 chhio7 i kng, Chit8 lang5 chit8 kak.” 
 Pit-kou khoaN3 i hiah chhut-lat8 khau kau3 lau5 koaN7, ka7 i kong2, “An2-ni oe7 choe3-tit, li2 chaiN2-iuN7 chiah chhut-lat8 ?” Bong2-chhi7 kong2, “TiaN2 si7 ti7 goa2 chit kak, goa2 tioh8 khau kau3 chin chheng-khi3, an2-ni chiu7-si7 chhio7 kng.”Pit-kou chhio3 kong2, “Li2 khau tiaN2 chheng-khi3, bo5 chheng-khi3, bo5 lang5 oe7 chai,”Bong2-chhi7 soe3 siaN in3 kong2, “Chu2 oe7 chai. ”Pit-kou hit si5 khi3 chian chit8 te3 gu5-bah, sim-lai7 siuN7, “Chu2 te3 ti7 goa2 chit kak, goa2 tioh8 chu2 chin phang thang chhio7 kng ti7 goa2 sou2 tiam3 e5 sou2-chai7.” Chu-koaN jit8-tau3 chiah8 gu5-bah ka7 Pit-kou kong2, “Li2 sou2 chu2 chit te3 gu5-bah chin ho2 chiah8.” Pit-kou thiaN-kiN3 hoaN-hi2 kong2, “Goa2 chu2 ho2 chiah8 si7 in-ui7 thiaN Bong2-chhi7 e5 oe7,”chiu7 chiong khau tiaN2 e5 su7 kong2 hou7 Chu-koaN thiaN. 
 Chu-koaN hit si5 teh ut saN, seng-khu sian7 m7 ai3 koh ut, thiaN Pit-kou e5 oe7 chiu7 siuN7, “U7 iaN2 saN ti7 goa2 chit kak, goa2 tioh8 ut kau3 chin ho2-se3.” Hit nia2 saN si7 Gou7 Kou-niu5 e5, Gou7 Kou-niu5 chheng7, o-lo2 kong2, “Chu-koaN, li2 chit nia2 saN ut liau2 chin sui2.” Chu-koaN chiu7 kong2-khi2 Bong2-chhi7 khau tiaN2 e5 su7 hou7 i thiaN. Bo5 loa7 ku2 u7 lang5 lai5 chhiaN2 Gou7 Kou-niu5 khi3 kiaN5-kiaN5 thit-tho5, Gou7 Kou-niu5 kong2, “Goa2 beh khi3 ki5-to2 hoe7 ti7 goa2 chit kak.”I e5 peng5-iu2 bo5 beng5-pek8, Gou7 Kou-niu5 chiu7 kong2 hou7 i chai, sou2 eng-kai tioh8 kiaN5 e5, lan2 chin7 pun2-hun7 lai5 kiaN5 i, chiu7-si7 chhio7 kng ti7 lan2 e5 sou2-chai7. In peng5-iu2 kong2 i beh kap i khi3 hu3 ki5-to2 hoe7. Le2-pai3 soah bok8-su lai5 ka7 in kong2, “Goa2 hoaN-hi2 lin2 nng7 lang5 lai5, lin2 bo5 lai5 chiu7 bo5 lang5 thang khi2 si-tiau7.” Gou7 Kou-niu5 to3-lai5 ai3 khi3 khun3, koh siuN7, “Goa2 e5 lau7-bu2 u7 chit8 siang oe5 chhiah iau2-be7 ho2 thang kong2 si7 ti7 goa2 chit kak, goa2 beh chhiah hou7 i chheng7.” In lau7-bu2 khoaN3 hoaN-hi2, o-lo2 i e5 kip-ke3, Gou7 Kou-niu5 chiu7 chiong Bong2-chhi7 khau tiaN2 e5 su7 kong2 hou7 i e5 lau7-bu2 thiaN. Teh kong2 e5 si5 kau3-hoe7 e5 chip-su7 lai5 beh theh8 Soan-to7 hoe7 e5 gun5. Gou7 Kou-niu5 e5 lau7-bu2 u7 tiaN7-tioh8 beh hian3 chap8 khou, khi3 theh8 e5 si5 sim-lai7 siuN7 “Chap8 he3 e5 gin2-na2 oe7 hiau2-tit chiau3 i sou2 oe7 lai5 eng5-kng Siong7-te3, goa2 bo5 i e5 chin7-tiong, tioh8 hian3 khah ke.” Chiu7 theh8 chhut ji7-gou7 khou gun5 lai5 hou7 chip-su7 siu. 
 Hit mi5 goa2 bang7 thiN-teng2 nng7 e5 thiN-sai3 saN kap kong2 oe7. Chit8 e5 thiN-sai3 kong2, “Bong2-chhi7 kin-a2-jit8 hian3 ji7-gou7 khou hou7 Siong7-te3 hoe7.” Hit e5 thiN-sai3 in3 kong2, “Bong2-chhi7 bo5 gun5, beh thai3 u7 ji7-gou7 khou thang hian3 ? ”In3 kong2, “Bong2-chhi7 chiau3 i sou2 oe7 chin7 lat8 khau tiaN2, Chu2 chiu7 pou2 i sou2 boe7 kau3, chiu7-si7 chiong Gou7 Ko-niu5 e5 lau7-bu2 sou2 hian3 e5, sng3 Bong2-chhi7 e5 i3-su3.” 
 Bong2-chhi7 long2 m7 chai lang5 kap thiN-sai3 teh khoaN3 i, jit8-jit8 bong ke-su7, put-si5 gim5 si kong2, 
 “Chit se3-kan si7 ou-am3, Na2 chhin-chhiuN7 ou-bak8; Lan2 tioh8 chhio7 I kng, Chit8 lang5 chit8 kak.” 
 20. Ka-ki7 khng3 I e5 m7 tioh8 boe7 tit-tioh8 Hok-khi3 
 U7 chit8 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 mia5 kio3 Giok8-a2. I e5 pe7-bu2 si7 keng3-khian5 sin3 Chu2 e5 lang5, put-chi2 ti3-i3 ka3 kiaN2-ji5 bat Seng3-keng, ai3 in chin-chiaN3 choe3 Ia-sou Ki-tok e5 hak8-seng. 
 Giok8-a2 u7 khi3 lu2-oh8 thak8 chheh. Hit keng oh8 e5 hak8-seng kong2, “in e5 sian-siN chit8 lang5 beh khi3 pat8 ui7 choe3 sian-siN; tai7-ke ai3 boe2 chit8 hang7 mih8 sang3 i, tiaN7-tioh8 tak8 lang5 tioh8 toe5 chiN5. Giok8-a2 thiaN-kiN3 liau2 sim lioh8-a2 bo5 peng5-an. In-ui7 i bo5 chiN5, kiaN-liau2 bo5 toe5 oe7 kian3-siau3.” I chiu7 kong2, “Goa2 bo5 chiN5 thang toe5.” Kap I tang5 teng2 e5 hak8-seng kong2, “Goan2 khah soe3-han3 m7 sai2 toe5 choe7, chong2-si7 tak8 lang5 tioh8 toe5, li2 bo5 chiN5 thang toe5 ka7 lin2 lau7-bu2 tho2, I tek-khak oe7 hou7 li2.” 
 Giok8-a2 siuN7 bo5 tek-khak beh hou7 goa2. In-ui7 i e5 lau7-bu2 tiaN7-tioh8 tak8 le2-pai3 Pai3-lak8 eng7 tam7-poh8 chiN5 hou7 i kap i e5 hiaN-ti7 chi2-be7, ka7 in kong2, “Chit e5 iN5 m7-thang liam-piN theh8 liam-piN khai, tioh8 soe3-ji7 eng7, in-ui7 chit e5 chiN5 i2-goa7 long2 bo5 beh koh hou7 lin2.” Giok8-a2 tak8 le2-pai3 Pai3-lak8 theh8 chiN5, sui5-si5 chhin3-chhai2 khai, taN long2 bo5 poaN3 e5 iN5. 
 Hit jit8 to3-khi3 in tau, Giok8-a2 ka7 in lau7-bu2 kong2, “Tong Kou-niu5 beh khi3 pat8-ui7 ka3 oh8, lu2-oh8 e5 hak8-seng ai3 boe2 chit8 hang7 mih8 sang3 i, goa2 ai3 tho2 tam7-poh8 chiN5 thang toe5, m7-chai li2 hoaN-hi2 hou7 goa2 a2-bo5 ?” 
 In lau7-bu2 kong2, “Pai3-lak8 hou7 li2 e5 chiN5 li2 na7 iau2 u7 chiu7 thang toe5, na7 bo5 chiu7 goa2 m7 ai3 koh hou7 li2.” 
 Giok8-a2 kong2, “Pai3-lak8 e5 chiN5 bo5--lah ! Koh tak8 lang5 toe5 goa2 bo5, kiam2 m7-si7 kian3-siau3 ?” 
 In lau7-bu2 kong2, “Goa2 bo5 beh hou7 li2, koh li2 m7-sai2 khoa3-i3, li2 m7-bat kap Tong Sian-siN thak8 chheh, i si7 ka3 lak8 teng2, li2 si7 thak8 nng7 teng2, han2-tit saN-tu2, li2 ai3 toe5, m7-si7 in-ui7 li2 keng3-thiaN3 i, si7 in-ui7 pat8 lang5 toe5, li2 bo5 hun7, kiaN kian3-siau3 na7-tiaN7.” 
 Giok8-a2 m7-kaN2 koh tho2, chong2 si7 ai3 tit-tioh8 chiN5. 
 Ke3 jit8 Giok8-a2 kap in sio2-be7 khi3 in goa7-ma2 tau, goa7-ma2 e5 chhu3 si7 kun7-kun7. Giok8-a2 chin7 ai3 khi3 hia thit-tho5, in-ui7 in ma2 chin7 thiaN3 i. 
 Hit jit8 koh khah hoaN-hi2 khi3, ng3-bang7 in ma2 eng7 chiN5 hou7 i, Chong2-si7 ma2 long2 bo5, i ia7 m7-kaN2 tho2. 
 Kau3 am3 beh to3-khi3, Giok8-a2 jip8 khun3 pang5 khoaN3 toh-teng2 u7 chiN5, bo5 lang5 ti7-teh, i chiu7 kin2-kin2 chhun chhiu2 theh8 chiN5 khng3 ti7 saN-a2 lai7, chau2 kau3 mng5 khau2, chiu7 kiaN koh sim siuN7, goa2 na7 theh8 chiah-e5 chiN5 chiu7-si7 choe3 chhat8, chiu7 kin2-kin2 oat8 jip8-khi3, beh he7 chiN5 ti7 goan5 ui7, khoaN3 khun3 pang5 u7 lang5 ti7 teh, chiu7 m7 kaN2 jip8, chau2 kau3 chau3-kha eng7 chiN5 hiat ti7 chau3 teng2. To3-khi3 e5 si5 i chiu7 siuN7, kai-chai3 bo5 thau-theh8 hiah-e5 chiN5, che si7 Siong7-te3 kiu3 goa2 bo5 ham7-loh8 choe7. 
 Ke3 jit8 iu5-goan5 khi3 oh8 nih8, pang3-he7 e5 si5 to3-lai5, in lau7-bu2 ka7 i kong2, “Giok8-a2, lin2 ma2 ai3 li2 koh khi3 in tau, m7-chai sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3, li2 e5 ji7-chi2 thang kap li2 khi3, teh beh am3, m7-thang ian5-chhian5.” 
 Giok8-a2 hoaN-hi2 in-ui7 iau2 teh ng3-bang7 chiN5, long2 bo5 phah-sng3 si7 i e5 ma2 khun3 pang5 toh-teng2 e5 chiN5 chhe7 bo5, chiu7 kio3 i lai5 mng7 i u7 theh8 a2 bo5. 
 Kau3 chhu3 in goa7-ma2 ka7 Giok8-a2 e5 ji7-chi2 mia5 kio3 Jin5-ai3 kong2, “Jin5-ai3 li2 khi3 hoe-hng5 kiaN5-kiaN5, goa2 u7 chit8 ku3 oe7 ai3 mng7 Giok8-a2.” Jin5-ai3 khi3 liau2 Giok8-a2 in ma2 chiu7 mng7 i kong2, “Li2 cha7-hng u7 thau-theh8 chiN5 bo5 ? Li2 na7 u7, tioh8 jin7, m7-thang kong2 peh8-chhat8.” 
 Giok8-a2 kong2, “Goa2 bo5 thau-theh8 chiN5.” 
 In ma2 kong2, “Goa2 ti7 khun3 pang5 toh teng2, goa2 chai, jip8 khun3 pang5--e5 , si7 li2 na7-tiaN7, long2 bo5 pat8 lang5, li2 to3-khi3 liau2, goa2 beh theh8 chiN5 eng7, i2-keng bo5 lah.” 
 Giok8-a2 tiam7-tiam7 bo5 kong2-oe7. I si7 chin gong7, i na7 kong2, “Goa2 tai7-seng u7 theh8, au7-lai5 m7 kaN2, chiu7 koh he7 ti7 chau3-kha,” in ma2 kaN2 bo5 sim2-mih8 hiam5, Chong2-si7 i long2 m7 kong2, in ma2 pek i tioh8 jin7, i tit8-tit8 kong2, “Goa2 bo5 choe3 chhat8,” kau3 be2 in ma2 ka7 i kong2 tioh8 to3-khi3. 
 Giok8-a2 kap in ji7-chi2 to3-khi3, ti7 lou7-nih8 hut-jian5 toa7-siaN hau2, in ji7-chi2 mng7 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3, i m7 kong2. U7 chit8 e5 lau7 sian-siN ti7 lou7-nih8 khoaN3-kiN3 hit nng7 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-a2, soe3-han3 teh hau2, i chiu7 hiam5 Jin5-ai3 kong2, “Li2 m7-thang chhong3-ti7 lin2 sio2-be7.” 
 Jin5-ai3 ka7 Giok8-a2 kong2, “Li2 ti7 koe-lou7 m7-thang toa7-siaN hau2, lang5 giau5-gi5 goa2 phaiN2 khoan2-thai7 li2, goa2 chin kian3-siau3, goa2 ia7 m7 chai li2 hau2 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3.” 
 Kau3 in tau Giok8-a2 iau2 teh hau2, in lau7-bu2 mng7 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3, Giok8-a2 kong2, “Goan2 ma2 kong2, goa2 si7 choe3 chhat8 , thau-theh8 chiN5.” In lau7-bu2 bo5 hoaN-hi2 kong2, “Tek-khak bo5 chit e5 su7, li2 m7-bat thau-theh8 mih8, choe3 li2 an-sim, goa2 khah am3 beh khi3 lin2 ma2 tau ka7 i kong2.” 
 Bin5-a2-chai3 Giok8-a2 in lau7-bu2 mng7 i kong2, “Giok8-a2, lin2 ma2 kong2, chiN5 i2-keng chhe7-tioh8, Chong2-si7 i eng7 chiN5 he7 ti7 khun3 pang5 e5 toh-teng2, hoan2-tng2 ti7 chau3-kha chhe7-tioh8, i kong2 li2 i2-goa7 bo5 lang5 jip8 khi3 khun3 pang5, tek-khak si7 li2 theh8 hiah-e5 chiN5, li2 u7 theh8 bo5 ?” 
 Giok8-a2 kong2, “Long2 bo5 bong-tioh8, long2 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3. ”I an2-ni kong2 peh8-chhat8,sim lioh8-a2 kiaN, chai i sou2 choe3 si7 m7-tioh8. Chong2-si7 au7-lai5 lang5 long2 bo5 mng7 hit e5 chiN5 e5 tai7-chi3, i chiu7 bo5 ku2 long2 boe7 ki3-tit. I sui-jian5 boe7 ki3-tit, Siong7-te3 long2 bo5 boe7 ki3-tit. 
 Teng2-bin7 sou2 sia2 Giok8-a2 e5 su7, hit si5 i si7 poeh-he3, chit e5 tai7-chi3 si7 ji7-geh8 tu2-tioh8, kau3 chap8-it geh8, Seng3-sin5 chiu7 kam2-hoa3 i e5 sim, hou7 i koh ki3-tit i e5 choe7. 
 Chit e7-hng i to2 ti7 bin5-chhng5 long2 boe7 khun3-tit, hut-jian5-kan siuN7 tioh8 i teng2-jit8 u7 kong2 peh8-chhat8, koh siuN7 seng3-chheh u7 kong2, “Ai3 kong2 peh8-chhat8 oe7 e5 lang5 tioh8 koaN2 i chhut siaN5 goa7.” 
 I chai siaN5 chiu7-si7 thian-tong5, koaN2 chhut e5 tioh8 loh8 te7-gek8, i chiu7 kiaN kau3 m7 kaN2 khun3, kiaN-liau2 khun3 e5 si5 oe7 si2. I ai3 ki5-to2 kiu5 Siong7-te3 sia3-bian2, i e5 ki5-to2, an2-ni hoan-lai5 hoan-khi3, chin bo5 peng5-an. I e5 lau7-bu2 lai5 sun5, ka7 gin2-na2 kah-phe7, khoaN3 Giok8-a2 bo5 khun3 chiu7 mng7, “Li2 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3 ? U7 phoa3-piN7 a2-bo5 ?” 
 Giok8-a2 ai3 ka7 lau7-bu2 kong2, Chong2-si7 m7-kaN2. In lau7-bu2 siuN7 kaN2 si7 iau, chiu7 khi3 chhong3 tiam2-sim hou7 i chiah8. Giok8-a2 chiah8 tiam2-sim liau2 chiah khun3. 
 Ke3 jit8 long2 bo5 siuN7 chit e5 tai7-chi3, kau3 am3 khi3 khun3 chiu7 koh chai3 siuN7, iu5-goan5 chin kiaN, kui2 na7 jit8 long2 si7 an2-ni, jit8-si5 thit-tho5 a2-si7 thak8-chheh, chiah oe7 pang3-sim, to2 ti7 bin5-chhng5 boe7 an-sim. Lau7-bu2 boe7 hiau2-tit, m7-chai i e5 cha-bou2 kiaN2 u7 sim2-mih8 piN7 chiah m7-ai3 khun3, u7-si5 che7 ti7 i e5 bin5-chhng5 piN kap i kong2 oe7, u7-si5 chhoa7 kau3 ka-ki7 e5 bin5-chhng5 khun3, Giok8-a2 ti7 lau7-bu2 e5 sin-piN chiu7 khah peng5-an. 
 Kau3 chit8 e5 e7-hng Giok8-a2 tong3-boe7-tiau5 lau5 bak8-sai2, ka7 in lau7-bu2 kong2, “Goa2 chin kiaN m7 kaN2 khun3, in-ui7 choe7 chin tang7, kiaN-liau2 khun3 e5 si5 si2, chiu7 loh8 te7-gek8.” 
 In lau7-bu2 in3 kong2, “Li2 sui-jian5 u7 kiaN5 choe7-choe7 hang7 m7 tioh8, li2 na7 kam-goan7 jin7 choe7, Siong7-te3 tai3-liam7 Kiu3-chu2 e5 kong-lo5 hoaN-hi2 sia3-bian2 li2 e5 choe7, soe2-tu5 li2 e5 phaiN2.” In lau7-bu2 chiu7 kap i saN-kap ki5-to2, Chong2-si7 Giok8-a2 siuN7 i m7 kaN2 jin7 choe7, na7-si7 bo5 jin7 choe7, chiu7 ki5-to2 bo5 lou7-eng7, i ai3 kong2 i e5 sim-lai7 e5 kan-khou2, chhui3 m7 kong2. 
 Kau3 koh chit8 e5 e5-hng i siuN7 beh ki5-to2 kiu5 Siong7-te3 hou7 i kam-goan7 jin7, i chiu7 to2 ti7 bin5-chhng5 theng3-hau7 in lau7-bu2 lai5, chiu7 tit8-tit8 ki5-to2 kiu5 Siong7-te3. In lau7-bu2 lai5 liau2, iu5-goan5 kong2 boe7 chhut. I e5 lau7-bu2 khoaN3 i e5 kan-khou2, chiu7 ka7 i kong2, “Giok8-a2 m7 chai li2 u7 choe3 sim2-mih8 m7 tioh8 ? Li2 kong2, choe7 tang7 iau2-be7 kong2 sim2-mih8 choe7. ” 
 Giok8-a2 tiam7-tiam7, lau7-bu2 ia7 bo5 koh mng7. Theng5 chit8 hun ku2, Giok8-a2 chiu7 kong2, “Goa2 u7 choe3 chit8 hang7 chin m7 tioh8, chiu7-si7 kong2 peh8-chhat8. ” In lau7-bu2 kong2, “Li2 na7 jin7 choe7 , Siong7-te3 chiu7 beh sia3-bian2 li2 e5 choe7, li2 na7 khng3-bat8 li2 e5 choe7, chiu7 bo5 tit-tioh8 peng5-an.” 
 Giok8-a2 kong2, “Chit e5 tai7-chi3, i2-keng chin ku2.” In lau7-bu2 kong2, “Giok8-a2 lin2 goa7-ma2 e5 chiN5, li2 u7 thau-theh8 a2-bo5 ?” 
 Giok8-a2 kong2, “Goa2 bo5 thau-theh8, goa2 u7 tai7-seng theh8, au7-lai5 m7-kaN2, khi3 heng5 he7 ti7 chau3-kha.” 
 In lau7-bu2 kong2, “Li2 hit si5 siaN2-su7 m7 jin7, kong2 hiah choe7 peh8-chhat8 oe7.” 
 Giok8-a2 cheng7-cheng7. 
 In lau7-bu2 kong2, “Li2 taN tioh8 khi3 ka7 lin2 lau7-pe7 kong2, i iau2-be7 khi3 khun3, iau2 ti7 oh8-pang5.” 
 Giok8-a2 m7 kaN2 the, ia7 si7 chin m7 ai3 khi3 ka7 in pe7 kong2, sim phok8-phok8 chheng2, un5-un5-a2 loh8 lau5-thui kiaN5 kau3 oh8-pang5 e5 mng5-khau2, chiu7 m7 kaN2 jip8. 
 In pe7 thiaN-kiN3 lang5 ti7 mng5-khau2, chiu7 kio3 kong2, “Sim2-mih8 lang5 ?” 
 Giok8-a2 soe3 siaN kong2, “Si7 goa2.” 
 In pe7 koh mng7, “Goa2 si7 chi7 chui7 ?” Chiu7 khui mng5 khoaN3 Giok8-a2 ti7 hia, chiu7 ki5-koai3, pho7 i jip8 lai5 kong2, “Sim-koaN kiaN2, sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3--ah ! Li2 siaN2-su7 m7 khi3 khun3 ?” 
 Giok8-a2 lau5 bak8-sai2. In lau7-bu2 te3 i lai5 kong2, “Giok8-a2 m7 si7 ho2 e5 gin2-a2, li2 oe7 ki3-tit kui2-na7 geh8-jit8 cheng5 in goa7-ma2 kong2, u7 theh8 i e5 chiN5, i kong2 i long2 m7-bat bong, ia7 m7-bat khoaN3, chiah-e5 oe7 si7 peh8-chhat8, kau3 chit-chun7 i tu2-a2 u7 jin7.” 
 Giok8-a2 in pe7 teh pho7 i, thiaN-kiN3 chiah-e5 oe7 chiu7 kin2-kin2 pang3 i loh8-khi3, i e5 bin7 chin iu-bun7, i che7 loh8-khi3 eng7 chhiu2 kham3 i e5 bin7 kong2, “Ai ah ! Goa2 e5 soe3 cha-bou2 kiaN2 ! Goa2 e5 soe3 cha-bou2 kiaN2 ! ”Giok8-a2 e5 lau7-bu2 ia7 lau5 bak8-sai2. Giok8-a2 ti7 hia teh khia7, kan-khou2 kau3-kek8, theng5 tiap8-a2-ku2 in lau7-bu2 kong2 , “KaN2 tioh8 hou7 Giok8-a2 khi3 khun3, i si7 chheng7 khun3 saN na7-tiaN7, kiaN-liau2 oe7 koaN5.”Chiu7 ka7 i kong2, tioh8 koh chiuN7 lau5-teng2. 
 Giok8-a2 sui-jian5 u7 kian3-siau3, u7 iu-bun7, chong2-si7 i e5 sim-toe2 u7 peng5-an, kui2-na7 jit8 m7-bat kau3 hiah peng5-an, i chiu7 kui7-loh8 ti7 bin5-chhng5 piN ki5-to2 kiu5 Siong7-te3 sia3-bian2 i e5 choe7, ki5-to2 liau2 chiu7 to2-teh khun3. 
 Bin5-a2 cha2-khi2, Giok8-a2 khi2-lai5 sim tang7-tang7 m7-kaN2 kiN3 tioh8 pe7 bu2 e5 bin7. Cha2-khi2 chiah8 pa2 in lau7-bu2 chiu7 ka7 i kong2 , “Giok8-a2 kin-a2-jit8 bian2 khi3 thak8-chheh.” 
 In toa7-chi2 mng7, “Giok8-a2 bo5 khi3 thak8-chheh si7 chaiN2-iuN7 ?” In lau7-bu2 bo5 in3 , theng3-hau7 gin2-a2 long2 khi3 oh8--nih8 chiu7 ka7 Giok8-a2 kong2, “Li2 kap goa2 khi3 goa7-ma2 tau.” 
 Giok8-a2 cheng7-cheng7 te3 in lau7-bu2 khi3, in lau7-bu2 chiu7 ka7 in ma2 kong2, “Giok8-a2 cha2-si5 u7 kong2 peh8-chhat8 .”In goa7-ma2 bo5 sim2-mih8 hiam5 kong2, “Che si7 goa2 i2-keng chai, taN Siong7-te3 e5 Sin5 kam2-hoa3 i e5 sim hou7 ka-ki7 jin7, tui3 an2-ni thang ng3-bang7 i chin chiaN3 u7 hoan2-hoe2.” 
 Au7-lai5 in lau7-bu2 chhoa7 Giok8-a2 khi3 chit8 e5 chhai5-hong5 e5 tiam3, chhai5-hong5 hit-si5 teh choe3 saN nia2 saN, chiu7-si7 beh hou7 Giok8-a2 kap i nng7-e5 toa7-chi2 thang chheng7. In lau7-bu2 ka7 chhai5-hong5 kong2, “Giok8-a2 e5 saN bian2 choe3, i chit-chun7 bo5 khiam3-eng7.” To3-khi3 e5 si5 ka7 i kong2, “Li2 ai3 thau-theh8 mih8, lang5 na7 beh chhiaN2 li2, goa2 m7 kaN2 hou7 li2 khi3, an2-ni m7-bian2 choe3 sin saN hou7 li2” 
 Hit e5-hng5 in pe7 kio3 i lai5 ka7 i kong2, “Giok8-a2 tui3 chit-si5 ‘Gin2-na2 Geh8 Po3’ m7 koh hou7 li2 siu.” 
 Che si7 in-ui7 Giok8-a2 chin3-pou7 thak8-chheh in pe7 u7 kong2, tak8 geh8-jit8 beh boe2 geh8 po3 siuN2 i. “Gin2-na2 Geh8 Po3,”si7 chin sui2 e5 chheh, u7 choe7-choe7 ang-a2 tou5, ia7 u7 ho2 thak8 e5 kou3-su7. 
 Giok8-a2 put-chi2 po2-sioh, tak8 geh8-jit8 tit-tioh8, i e5 sim hoaN-hi2 kau3-kek8. I e5 hiaN ti7 chi2-be7 tak8-e5 ia7 chin ai3 khoaN3, ia7 u7 chioh tang5 oh8 e5 hak8-seng khoaN3. Tak8 geh8 thak8 liau2 u7 soe3-ji7 siu, kau3 u7 lak8 pun2 chiu7 u7 theh8 kau3 chheh tiam3 kap sui2-sui2 e5 phe5. 
 Giok8-a2 i2-keng tit-tioh8 14 geh8-jit8 e5 po3, taN u7 nng7 e5 toa7 pun2 chiu7-si7 lak8 pun2 kap choe3 chit8-pun2, ia7 u7 nng7 e5 thiah pun2. 
 Hiah-e5 chheh si7 Giok8-a2 e5 sim sou2 ai3, siong5-siong5 theh8 chhut-lai5 thak8, lang5 lai5 i ai3 pun in khoaN3. TaN in pe7 kong2, “In-ui7 li2 kong2 peh8-chhat8, m7 koh hou7 li2 ,” i ia7 chai che si7 tioh8. Tui3 chit si5 i2-au7 hiah-e5 chheh si7 i sou2 m7-ai3 khoaN3 i theh8 khi3 khng3 ti7 chheh-tu5 e5 chheh au7. U7-si5 in chi2-be7 ai3 mng7, “Giok8-a2 lan2 pe7 siaN2-su7 m7 koh boe2, ‘Gin2-na2 Geh8-Po3’ hou7 li2 ?”I ia7 bo5 oe7 thang in3. 
 Giok8-a2 kau3 choe3 toa7-lang5 na7 khoaN3-kiN3 hiah-e5 chheh, chiu7 sui5-si5 ki3-tit i cheng5 e5 m7-tioh8, sim chiu7 tin2-tang7, chit8 hang7 si7 ui7 tioh8 i e5 choe7 iu-bun7 kian3-siau3, koh chit8 hang7 si7 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3 hit si5 ka3 i kui2 na7 hang7, chiu7-si7 i chit8-si3 lang5 bo5 koh boe7 ki3-tit. 
 Chit8 hang7 i tui3 hit si5 chai Siong7-te3 si7 kun7-kun7 e5 Siong7-te3 tak8 hang7 chai, Siong7-te3 thiaN3 i, m7 kam hou7 i khng3-bat8 i e5 choe7, ai3 i tit-tioh8 chheng-khi3 e5 sim. Koh tui3 hit si5 chai “Siong7-te3 sia3 i e5 choe7, kham3 i e5 choe7-koa3, che lang5 u7 hok-khi3” Si 32: 1,2. Na7 si7 “ka-ki7 khng3 i e5 m7 tioh8 boe7 tit-tioh8 hok-khi3.” Chin 28:13. 
 21. Gau5 e5 Hu7-jin5-lang5 Kam2-kek Tiong7-hu 
 Kui2 ni5 cheng5 ti7 Tai7-bi2 kok e5 chit8 sou2-chai7 teh sin khui pou-thau5. U7 chit8 e5 pai3 Siong7-te3 e5 choh-sit lang5, chhiaN3 chin choe7 kang teh khui hng5. I ai3 than3 ho2 thiN kin2 khui hou7 i liau2, sou2-i2 tak8 cha2-khi2 chiu7 cha2-cha2 kio3 kang khi3 khui. I e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 na7 chu2-sek8, chiu7 pun5 hou7-thau5 kio3 in to3 lai5 chiah8. 
 Chit e5 choh-sit lang5 peng5-siong5 tak8 cha2-khi2 u7 kap i e5 ke-lai7 kap i e5 kang thak8 Seng3-chheh ki5-to2; Chong2-si7 in-ui7 beh koaN2 kang soah boe7 kou3-tit choe3 le2-pai3. 
 I e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 i khah ti3-i3 se3-kan e5 chiN5-chai5 boe7 kou3-tit hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3, chiu7 khou2-khng3 i, na7-si7 i long2 m7 thiaN; chiah siuN7 chit8 e5 hoat-tou7 hou7 i e5 tiong7-hu khoaN3 oe7 ke2-piN3 a2-boe7. Ke3 cha2-khi2, chit e5 choh-sit lang5 iu5-goan5 cha2-cha2 kio3 kang khi3 khui hng5. Kau3 jit8 chin oaN3 long2 bo5 thiaN-kiN3 pun5 ho7-thau5, tak8-e5 iau kau3 kha nng2 chhiu2 nng2. To3-lai5 kau3 te3 khoaN3 chit8 te3 toh khang-khang iah8 bo5 pai5 mih8-phe3 oaN2 phiat, i e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 choe3 i cheng7-cheng7 teh thak8 Seng3-chheh. Choh-sit lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 an2-ni chiu7 jiong2 kong2, “Eh ! iah8 png7 ti7 tah-loh8 ? ”I e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 in3 i kong2, “Goa2 khoaN3 lin2 chiah bo5 eng5, phah-sng3 bo5 eng5 thang chiah8.” 
