 Choh-sit-lang5 koh kong2, “Ho2, ho2, seng khi3 chu2 lai5 chiah8, chiong kim i2-au7 put-koan2 u7 eng5, bo5 eng5, tek-khak beh choe3 le2-pai3.” I e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 chiu7 khi3 chu2. Tui3 hit-tiap8 chin7 chit-si3-lang5 i tak8 cha2-khi2 u7 thak8 Seng3-chheh, ki5-to2. 
